 <title>Compost 101 at Moreno Farms, Minneapolis</title>
 <link>http://understory.org/composting-moreno-farms</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;
&lt;img src=&quot;/files/understory/images/compost_mf_1.jpg&quot; border=&quot;10&quot; alt=&quot;compostini&quot; hspace=&quot;10&quot; vspace=&quot;10&quot; width=&quot;150&quot; height=&quot;200&quot; align=&quot;right&quot; /&gt;Reed Aubin of Understory held a &amp;quot;how to compost&amp;quot; class 8-12-2010 at Moreno Farms, Minneapolis. We were unable to provide complete information at the workshop, so we will followup here with some additional tips and tidbits.
